      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the atmosphere, but it feels a bit generic. I want the scene to feel more grounded in reality. Can you get more specific about the tension or the dynamics? Like, what are some of the specific things they'd be arguing about or discussing that would make the scene feel more authentic to a Black family specifically? Give me some more texture.",
