      "content": "i get the social stuff, but i'm also looking for those more visceral, raw details that people usually associate with these kinds of settings. like, if i wanted to lean into the more \"intense\" or \"unfiltered\" side of things—maybe some of the louder, more confrontational stuff you'd see in movies or even real life—how would that play out? what would the actual dialogue or behavior look like if they were being more \"real\" or less polite?",
